<i>adverb</i>: 휘황히 [휘황히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>휘황히 [휘황히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. radiant; dazzling; glittering</dd><br>
<dd>빛이 나서 눈부시게 번쩍이는 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being dazzlingly bright and shiny.</dd><br>
<dd>2. showily; slickly; deceptively</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 바르지 못하고 야단스러워서 믿을 수 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner in which the way one speaks or acts is improper and ostentatious, making it unreliable.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>